{"tid":164487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2017全球快樂報告　挪威最開心　香港升4位排75","createTime":"2017-03-20T16:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T02:00:20.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b1163936dd881fec6ff13c5965b50c4ea8b71b","tid":164487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170321/s00005/3cc396fec82514ffee07da1dcac0b0db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170321%2Fs00005%2F3cc396fec82514ffee07da1dcac0b0db.jpg&h=0ece39c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國「可持續發展網絡」（SDSN）發表「2017全球快樂報告」，挪威取代丹麥，成為全球最快樂國家或地區，香港排名比去年升了4位至75，美國則跌了1位排14。SDSN主管警告，特朗普政府的削減福利等經濟措拖，會令社會不平等問題加劇，令國民更不快樂。<br />\n<br />\nSDSN報告調查2014至2016年全球155個國家及地區人民的快樂水平，根據人均國內生產總值、健康壽命、自由、慷慨、社會支援及政府或商業有否貪腐6個因素來評分，10分為滿分。結果顯示，全球最快樂地方多是北歐國家，挪威由去年排第4升至今年的首位，緊隨其後的是丹麥和冰島。香港排第71，較去年排75名上升。中國由去年排第83升至今年的79。敘利亞、也門和撒哈拉以南非洲地區則最不快樂。<br />\n<br />\nSDSN主管、聯合國秘書長特別顧問薩克斯（Jeffrey Sachs）說：「快樂國家是在傳統指標中，繁榮和社會資本取得健康平衡，代表社會信任度高、不平等程度低，並對政府有信心。」<br />\n<br />\n美國排名下跌1位，薩克斯指出，美國名次下滑主要是因為不平等、不信任和貪腐。他表示，特朗普政府打算推出的經濟措施可能會令情況變得更壞，例如減富人稅、減醫保受保人數、減長者送餐服務等，目的是為了增加軍費，這只會令社會不平等增加，「我認為這些建議措施全走錯方向」。薩克斯建議各國效法阿聯酋等國，委任一名快樂部長，政府可就民眾的快樂程度作出量度、討論和分析。<br />\n<br />\n中國的排名雖比去年上升，不過報告指出，中國的人均GDP在過往25年雖然增長逾5倍，然而當今的人民「主觀幸福感」不見得高於1990年代，主要是因為現今失業率增加、社會保障減少等因素。"},{"pid":"ee5706bf07e157976a554072f932890940cc950c","tid":164487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170321/s00005/1490024606842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170321%2Fs00005%2F1490024606842&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5RFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=257e43bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170321%2Fs00005%2F1490024606842&h=b7bb80ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170321/s00005/1490024606842</a>"},{"pid":"ea8dff929ee39b20adcd5b292c12833ba9d46866","tid":164487,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"香港淪陷 邊個最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0738005e9c4a3b08990f79e255936d7ea613b918","tid":164487,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"香港第1名攞厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e872cfdc05f41bf23618e23bee6399f55197b3e7","tid":164487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4b3903e558ee4ee755e4da6f5b53473b0a9bd4","tid":164487,"uid":14329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ca8b31186e998cb4acb0d47220278f2143b18f","tid":164487,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"鄰近地區方面，新加坡排第26位，台灣排第33位，港人最愛的日本排第51位，中國則排第79位。"},{"pid":"e124c8e9d2d0a46696a101cb81d001646dc410d5","tid":164487,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港第1名攞厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e81e9930be1cce8260fd57352c8562436b11fb0","tid":164487,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"香港係體現到做黎唔知為乜既社會."},{"pid":"eb2f46ca4f1722f74bcce159604c8d7d1ac4784a","tid":164487,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:32:21.000Z","msg":"身為奴才實開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/